{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would come to camp, lead you down the quarry there, and there was a place there where they used to make you dig your own grave and shoot you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when somebody ran away, like I did on two occasions, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and if you weren't found within a specified time-- I don't know whether it was a day or two days-- they would take five people from either side of where you slept-- or if you have-- of if you had relatives, they would be right sleeping next to you-- they would take ten people and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Occasionally, the Judenrat, who were still in camp with us, were able to bribe the Germans and say, why would you take 10 productive people who were producing ammunition for the war effort and shoot them?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't you take out 10 people who are very sick from the sick barrack who are going to die anyway and shoot them?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So occasionally, this was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would take down 10 people, make them dig their graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they were finished, just shoot them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Occasionally, we used to work outside of the perimeter of the factories.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factories were fenced in with, I don't know, about a 6 or 8 meter-- foot fence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to sometimes go out and repair the-- the railway lines or unload a wagon of some kind of product outside the factory, like road building materials or something like this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on one such occasion, I could see the guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wasn't so watchful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew the town, the surroundings, and I snuck away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
